{
  "stem": "14156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I guess he-- he knew that the thing is going to come to an end, but he was still mean and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] killing people or-- or trying to keep the-- the Hitler idea up.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can remember that so many dead people were laying around.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had to carry them-- they made a big, you know, a hole to throw them in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People were nothing but skeletons and-- and bones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then there was one fellow-- he-- he had him walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And him-- he with his luger-- onto-- on the back on his head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he-- he told him to keep on going-- go!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the man knew it's gonna be his end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he begged-- please, Herr Unterscharfuhrer, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Don't, don't!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well, it didn't do no good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "One shot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I can-- I can never forget.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's like when you take a-- a sack of sugar or anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You hold it up, and let it go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Bang.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He dropped.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Just like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then somebody pushed him in, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then, at night, we-- we had to lay on the floors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In the beginning, I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But what happened was, everybody-- once you get up and you try to get back to the same place, there wasn't anything-- place to go back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And people did there-- there was no toilets, so they-- they did whatever they did in-- in-- the-- in those little cans and sprayed the thing over you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I said, no more-- not me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Like a barrack looks is-- there's rafters up on top.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's only.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I climbed up here, and I laid up there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Was about that wide.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
